properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 21 at 4:09AM EST until January 22 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the Gale Warning, north winds 25 to 30 kt with
gusts up to 45 kt and seas 11 to 16 feet expected. For the
Small Craft Advisory, north winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to
35 kt and seas 7 to 9 feet.

* WHERE...central Florida Atlantic coastal waters.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, until 2 PM EST this
afternoon. For the Gale Warning, from 2 PM this afternoon to 4
PM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for gale conditions.
